name: Artifact
description: Information about an artifact. The artifact can only be an IP.

children.name: as_owner
children.description: Owner of the Autonomous System to which the IP address belongs.

children.name: asn
children.description: Autonomous System Number to which the IP address belongs.

children.name: first_seen_time
children.description: First seen timestamp of the IP in the customer's environment.

children.name: jarm
children.description: The JARM hash for the IP address.

children.name: last_https_certificate
children.description: SSL certificate information about the IP address.

children.name: last_https_certificate_date
children.description: Most recent date for the certificate in VirusTotal.

children.name: last_seen_time
children.description: Last seen timestamp of the IP address in the customer's environment.

children.name: location
children.description: Location of the Artifact's IP address.

children.name: network
children.description: Network information related to the Artifact's IP address.

children.name: prevalence
children.description: The prevalence of the artifact within the customer's environment.

children.name: regional_internet_registry
children.description: RIR (one of the current RIRs: AFRINIC, ARIN, APNIC, LACNIC or RIPE NCC).

children.name: whois
children.description: WHOIS information as returned from the pertinent WHOIS server.

children.name: whois_date
children.description: Date of the last update of the WHOIS record in VirusTotal.
